com.preemptive.dasho.mapfile

Interface MapFileHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MapFileWriter

    public interface MapFileHandler
    Handler interface used to deal with the sequence of information found in a map file. The handler to structure the production or consumption of information in a map file regardless of its source. The methods should be called in the following order:
    • startFile() - exactly once
    • startClass() - zero or more times
      • method() - zero or more times
      • field() - zero or more times
    • endClass() - once for each startClass()
    • endFile() - exactly once
